      <p>This is the part people skip and regret. Before you upload a file to the SSC portal, the Income Tax site, or some college submission box, actually scroll through every page. A lot of these portals reject or silently mangle files, and once it's submitted you can't take it back. The same goes for the Xerox shop — hand them a sideways PDF and you'll get a stack of sideways printouts, plus a second trip and a second payment.</p>
