      <p>Now the annoying twist. Plenty of Indian portals don't just want a <em>shape</em>, they want exact <em>pixels</em>. Something like "photo must be 200x230 px" or "signature between 10 and 20 KB." Cropping alone won't put a number on your file. What it does is hand you a clean, correctly-shaped image with no junk around it, which is exactly what the resizer needs as input.</p>
